channel.title: Is uptime earned back?
channel.description: Can you earn uptime from the status page back..? Example: My current uptime is 99%. Will it ever go back to 100?

item.title: Is uptime earned back?
item.dc:creator: @it0ken1 it0ken1
item.description:
@it0ken1 wrote:

hippo429:

no it will never go back to 100% but it will never go to 0% use some math… if its been off for 1 minute you cant have it on 100% right? so you answer is no, but you could always keep it at 99% or if your at 1% you can get it back to 99% but not 100%

That’s not what others seem to be saying when I do research.
I understand your math but others aren’t saying that. Anyone else?
